{"pid":"c1b385357caaa141357deebc9101b92f9255e34c","tid":373394,"uid":68394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"有冇人知大概九月幾會有消息佢寫九月下旬"},{"pid":"e35eda64a70a8200b7d1bf7ae09750dbccfe9fd4","tid":373394,"uid":62985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成team 廿幾人，一季得幾個係新人，舊人都要照apply照in，讀緊書既肯定唔會請，fg有cs經驗就有機。<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢做過一季</blockquote><br />\n屌政府唔請就唔好比學生apply啦 勁多學生想做<br />\n利申 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為好似part time形式報更咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到短期full time返個半月嘅工都有咁多人apply</blockquote><br />\n我都夢見過<br />\n去到好多舊人頭幾日就踩盡做<br />\n最好笑係請一日假都要搞場大龍鳳<br />\n<br />\n佢地預你成個period一日假都唔會請的"},{"pid":"8308493310c0350dae3e8f672424a4275c759be4","tid":373394,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成team 廿幾人，一季得幾個係新人，舊人都要照apply照in，讀緊書既肯定唔會請，fg有cs經驗就有機。<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢做過一季</blockquote><br />\n屌政府唔請就唔好比學生apply啦 勁多學生想做<br />\n利申 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以為好似part time形式報更咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到短期full time返個半月嘅工都有咁多人apply</blockquote><br />\n我都夢見過<br />\n去到好多舊人頭幾日就踩盡做<br />\n最好笑係請一日假都要搞場大龍鳳<br />\n<br />\n佢地預你成個period一日假都唔會請的</blockquote><br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難得抽中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔請"},{"pid":"640885fd1937fb678d7e914f5181e87fdafdae33","tid":373394,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知大概九月幾會有消息佢寫九月下旬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常2X號"},{"pid":"107f1ecb0451252ad1d89167092ad0e8496fd76d","tid":373394,"uid":138045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":